###  Update monitoring config
###
### Update monitoring config
### @param workerName - Worker name (path)
### @param checkInterval - Interval in seconds (body, optional)
### @param thresholds - Threshold config (body, optional)
### @param alerting - Alerting config (body, optional)
### @returns Success message
###
PUT {{WORKER_API_URL}}/api/workers/{{workerName}}/monitoring/config
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "thresholds": {
    "errorRate": 1.0,
    "p95LatencyMs": 500
  }
}

###  Versions - register
###
### Register worker version
### @param workerName - Worker name (path)
### @param version - Semantic version object (body)
### @param migrationPath - Migration path (body, optional)
### @param eolDate - End of life date (body, optional)
### @param changelog - Changelog (body, optional)
### @param breakingChanges - Array of breaking changes (body, optional)
### @returns Success message
###
POST {{WORKER_API_URL}}/api/workers/{{workerName}}/versions
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "version": "1.2.0",
  "notes": "release notes"
}

