### @param initialTrafficPercent - Starting traffic percent (body)
### @param targetTrafficPercent - Target traffic percent (body)
### @param incrementPercent - Increment per step (body)
### @param incrementInterval - Seconds between increments (body)
### @param monitoringDuration - Seconds per step (body)
### @param errorThreshold - Error threshold (body)
### @param latencyThreshold - Latency threshold (body)
### @param minSuccessRate - Minimum success rate (body)
### @param autoRollback - Auto rollback flag (body)
### @returns Success message
###
POST {{WORKER_API_URL}}/api/workers/{{workerName}}/canary/start
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "percentage": 10
}

